{"id": 423, "genre": 1001, "title": "你最讨厌哪些微信习惯？", "description": "每天总有那么几个人，让你点开微信很心焦。", "record_count": 9997, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194615fjkAbN8i1xYMulhI.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-15T11:09:37Z", "options": [{"id": 3633, "content": "全文党，段子手", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 3636, "content": "转发各种不实谣言从不查证是否属实", "image": null, "praise_count": 863, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141911}, {"id": 3637, "content": "整天晒自己家小孩的~", "image": null, "praise_count": 234, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137843}, {"id": 3640, "content": "表里不一在微信里和在生活中判若两人", "image": null, "praise_count": 141, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133375}, {"id": 3639, "content": "出门了发一次 上网了发一次 吃东西了发一次 遛狗了发一次 不舒服了发一次 总之就是屁大点事儿都要发 平均每天10条 很烦的好吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 554, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141923}, {"id": 3644, "content": "朋友圈鸡汤文。", "image": "img/option/option/20160702200747f6jy5uFtM1wE2OAx.jpg", "praise_count": 333, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223}, {"id": 3306, "content": "喜欢把合适的不合适的各种聊天记录截屏转发", "image": null, "praise_count": 339, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3307, "content": "平时一句话不说，抢红包最积极", "image": null, "praise_count": 329, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3718, "content": "微博只要一有躁动 就使劲的往朋友圈里转 \n好玩吗！！能不能有些智商~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 3719, "content": "其实上述这些\n你们也曾经干过的吧\n快说！从实招来 抗拒从阉", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136181}, {"id": 3721, "content": "一句话分成几部分发送，你语气间断用个逗号不就好了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 51431}, {"id": 3727, "content": "图文不相关就是为了秀自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142256}, {"id": 3767, "content": "微商，代购，拿着产品秀自拍，发送验证是否删好友的信息，秀生活品质，散布紧迫感的谣言，不过这些都没什么，最可恶的是假红包，尼玛", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142410}, {"id": 3768, "content": "各种链接", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142461}, {"id": 3771, "content": "我就是经常晒娃的人，哈哈⋯⋯已经提示不喜欢的朋友直接屏蔽", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137418}, {"id": 3773, "content": "自拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43461}, {"id": 4005, "content": "干个啥都要都要发到盆友圈，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136143}, {"id": 4010, "content": "看完你们说的这些，我不知道要在朋友圈发什么了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132721}, {"id": 4119, "content": "不发最好，沉默是最好的武器，省的发什么都被归类。你们倒总结一下：朋友圈发啥内容最得体？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124265}, {"id": 3904, "content": "一本正经的胡说八道", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143295}, {"id": 3753, "content": "一天老是发自己好的一些小事 晒自拍  朋友圈当个人秀场", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142351}, {"id": 3751, "content": "有什么事情都爱晒，朋友圈每天爆满。每天说一堆不切实际的大道理，当老子是傻逼啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142339}, {"id": 3756, "content": "一般不作声，一买了点什么或者出去吃了点什么就各种晒，有意思么→_→", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5458}, {"id": 3754, "content": "我想全选，点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141254}, {"id": 3752, "content": "朋友圈只会刷自己头疼脑热 医院排不上号 满满负能量的", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115002}, {"id": 3876, "content": "自言自语", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114232}, {"id": 3807, "content": "只能说是各有各的看法吧 不然要满足以上所有的那大家都不要玩微信好了", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211415Ao0PniuwBXCt3zeY.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130370}, {"id": 3667, "content": "秀恩爱，仿佛全世界都只有ta的伴侣。你俩谁做饭好吃去哪潇洒了我并不想知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142014}, {"id": 3668, "content": "图文无关 秀自拍 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 171, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126812}, {"id": 3669, "content": "每天故作姿态的秀秀秀，还要特地装可怜", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 11320}, {"id": 3670, "content": "这些都不发，那朋友圈用来干嘛??", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114550}, {"id": 3675, "content": "不转的。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121509}, {"id": 3682, "content": "在微信上谈工作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126585}, {"id": 3685, "content": "把自己当意见领袖", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142094}, {"id": 3687, "content": "用性感风骚的美女图片做转载信息封面的", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141854}, {"id": 3688, "content": "海代有罪，鸡汤无理！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55104}, {"id": 3689, "content": "网络孝子", "image": null, "praise_count": 270, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130845}, {"id": 4725, "content": "看完之后，发朋友圈都得慎重了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144651}, {"id": 4514, "content": "我根本就上不了微信！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146958}, {"id": 6092, "content": "老子一个个去点上面这些段子的时候最烦…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149663}, {"id": 3841, "content": "成天正能量个没完", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114642}, {"id": 4099, "content": "天天看别人朋友圈，从来不评论或点赞。骨子里透着不屑，装尼马最清高，其实我去年买了个表！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144569}, {"id": 3845, "content": "鸡汤太多了", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234802l06VsSzjAn8WOEpc.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142687}, {"id": 3846, "content": "你特么发什么我点赞 我特么搞个活动让你点个赞怎么了 草", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142960}, {"id": 3847, "content": "不说了，罪孽深重。我是在说我吗？当然不是！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142970}, {"id": 3858, "content": "点赞狂魔，谁发的都顺手点赞，毫无心意。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133480}, {"id": 3861, "content": "说的跟你们啥都没发过一样。这种假装自己没做过的装逼最为讨厌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 143019}, {"id": 3870, "content": "睡觉时果断要开勿扰模式", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141931}, {"id": 20255, "content": "道德绑架；微商安利", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268540}, {"id": 40736, "content": "发朋友圈总是不发够9张图", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406909}]}